ActCanada Shipping Act, 2001
SubjectSmall Vessel Regulations
PrecisSMALL VESSEL REGULATIONS have been updated in order to better reflect the nature of the small vessel fleet in Canada and to ensure consistency with international standards respecting lifesaving appliances, vessel construction and compliance notices (otherwise known as Capacity or Conformity Labels).
